name: Satellite Warrior
desc:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner Synchro Monsters
When this card is Synchro Summoned: Target cards your opponent controls up to the number of Synchro Monsters in your GY; destroy those targets, also this card gains 1000 ATK. When this Synchro Summoned card is destroyed: Special Summon up to 3 Level 8 or lower "Warrior", "Synchron", and/or "Stardust" Synchro Monsters with different names from your GY. You can only use each effect of "Satellite Warrior" once per turn.
